2573,package_search does not allow solr's per-field facet parameters,icmurray,,"Solr allows its facet parameters to be specified on a per-field basis, eg. `facet.limit` applies to ''all'' facet fields, but solr allows it to be overriden for a specific field, eg. `facet.tags.limit`.

We don't support this at the moment because we have a whitelist of valid solr query parameters that we accept.  See `ckan.lib.search.query.VALID_SOLR_PARAMETERS`.",enhancement,new,awaiting triage,ckan-future,ckan,,[?d],rgrp,ckan,none
